reviews.review_text: I am not a fast food eater but there are times when you need it. Then there is, McDonald is and it is what it is. This location turnover is great which means foods are great. Never disappointed me once lol as Im typing, driving through here to get the boys some ice cones or mcflurry ha..
The drive thru messed up my order, but the manager Chris made it right in a very timely manner

Very good location, with lots of places to park. Definitely better than McDonalds in Chinatown downtown Vancouver which has no sits even inside. Also nice place to go after visiting Cineplex - Silver City riverport cinemas. Update after many visits noticed one constant: Regular staff in the evening working only if older women manager is in front or at the kitchen. If she is going anywhere staff stop working. Today at one time were no orders except my order with one ice cream cone and nobody did care about it for long time it was on the TV(Ive been standing in front of counter), when manager came and told staff to come to their place they started to work.
Just need to clean tables more
Always come here for my Coke Zero. Cheapest in town.

I would say typical of the chain but Im from the states and I dont have a lot of experience with McDonalds in Canada. The food was quick and hot. The staff were friendly for the brief interaction that we had. The lobby is much smaller than Im used to but there was still enough seating for everyone.

Ive only been here once and it was during the snowstorm where the Massey tunnel was blocked and Alex Fraser was closed over night. They were a good place to charge my phone and stress out until they closed and I had to relocate. The coffee I bought was good, so I dont really have any complaints
I like the staff.. they were friendly and quick with my order. The food was fresh and quality was very good. I will come again only because of the staff here.

Its safer than in Surrey and the food is better than the store in Metrotown. For sure I feel safe in this location. Im using mac app for ordering and never once a problem. Thumbs up for the cleanliness as well.
Staff is very friendly. Food was fresh and was in proper quantity and quality. Always prefer to go there as staff always help you with any doubt.
Staff accommodated our special requests. See photos.

Had some of the freshest French fries I ve ever had today. I come here for the free hour of EV charging at Ironwood and have noticed that the fries are almost never bad here. It s great. Free Wi-Fi too if you need it while you re enjoying these delicious fries. Curbside available until late in the evening if you want to sit in the car and minimize contact.

Saw a line up in the drive thru so we decided to go inside. Got our food rather quickly (probably quicker than what the drive thru would have been). Order was correct and food was nice and hot! Masks are still required here unless you are eating your food and there are ample safety barriers between you and the staff.
Great place to have kids over while super charging.
Waited 10 minutes for my artistic ice cream cone    . I heckin LOVE McDonalds!

Had a great experience with their employees came to help in a discriminating situation from an employee from save on foods who was racist to my family. The employees from McDonald s helped us greatly in the parking lot with that bad man. Thank you for your kindness and helping my family in that dangerous situation.

Visited on May 11th Mchappy Day and the staff there are always fast and friendly.  Tried the double Filet-O-Fish for the first time, with extra tartar sauce and it was delicious.  One of the best McDonalds in the entire lower mainland,  hands down.
Quicker to go inside sometimes, instead of the drive thru.  McGriddle is a unique taste option.

Great service. After waiting in line for not even 10 seconds someone offered to help me expedite my order through their new self service order screen. Walked me through the whole process and even explained their new create your burger process with table delivery. With regards to the environment, it was family friendly, clean and has a childrens play area.
Delicious food . I had a problem with my app and the manager their helped me with it. Really satisfied with my visit.
Great food and service. The staff were getting berated by a crazy woman mad about her large black coffee. And they handled them selves very professionally. And my order was top notch. Good job guys!
Who doesnt like McDonalds.  This place is great with an indoor playground,  best to let kids burn off some energy.
Mc donalds coffee.
Very helpfull staff. Good service and always serve fresh food

Compared to several other branches in lower mainland, the fries at this particular branch are almost always very hot, crunchy, and cooked all the way through. As someone who goes to McDonolds only because of the fries, I am willing to go slightly out of my way to get food from this branch rather than one closer to my current location or the one back home (120th street branch in Delta), in which 6-8/10 times the fries are either barely warm or undercooked, even if restaurant is packed for some gosh darn reason.
Wanted a quick stop for iced coffee as we head for a road trip. Drive thru line went super fast!

I ate here for breakfast today, me and my friend were expecting a regular Mc Donald experience, however we were greeted with a outstanding employee named Chris he asked everyone how there meal was, chatted with the elderly and made sure everyone was taken care of. Big ups to my man Chris the crew trainer
We love this McDonald s.  It is what it is.

Almost every weekday morning for the last 4 years I have used the Drive-thru at Steveston Hwy location.  I have always been served with courtesy and respect and my coffee is always perfect!  Jackie, at the cash window has always greeted me with a smile and a comment on the days weather.  I look forward to our morning conversations.

Found that when this location made a simple mistake (one patty not two) that I couldnt turn around to get fixed in that moment. They wanted to know what if anything they could do. This has not been my experience at other McDonalds locations. They offered any desert of my choosing which I thought was above and beyond. I got a sundae lol. Anytime I am in richmond and going to McDonalds this is the location I return to. Keep up the good work. WE DO NOTICE.
Good price excellent service
Great service, great price, tasty foods. Its mcdonalds, you guys know whats up Oh and this one was recently renovated so its extra nice inside

Its a McDonalds, the one thing that is extremely annoying about this location is that when you order drive-thru even if theres no one behind you theyll send you to a waiting area rather than just have you wait at the window stupid makes no sense.
Very busy .. Very Clean.. Nice staff Food : 5/5
Mc donalds with deliver to table service and a play place. Good with kids.
Come to the drive through from 6 to 10, Mathew is the best, clear speaking, perfect understanding,  pleasure to order from. And other crew is nice in the evening too, rarely making mistakes.
Friendly and helpful staff. They helped me to redeem my points on app.
Excellent location, the managers there go over and above if there are issues to make everything right!
Had a Mocca coffee.   In between shopping, just need a quick drink.  Staff quite diligent wiping tables.
Service is faster than some other McDonalds restaurants. Order is accurate. Broken tap in mens washroom, might need to fix that.
I like this place   quick drive by to pick up a quick meal. However if you  plan to drive back onto number 3 Rd you can only turn north (have to go around to go back South)
This is the best place. Staff was friendly and helpful.
Used to go here as a kid ;) my grandpa would always take me here to get fries and ice cream :o such pleasant memories...
Didnt have to wait long to order or receive it and the staff wasnt rude
Consistent and one of the top best quality fast food chain IMO, if service was consistent it would be top
Best place for 1$ ice cream
very fast service, faster than other mcdonalds.
THERES MC DONALDS EVERYWHERE :)
Been there drive through ordered food n coffee was fast service for my order.
Great place to dine in and take out. Safety and cleanliness at the above level. Enough parking.
QUICK TABLE SERVICE
Excellent service at the drive thru.  Quick, friendly and my order was complete.
Good fast service. Usual quality food too. Thumbs up here
no complaints! great run restaurant! kudos to the management =)
Its a good McDonalds.
I went to The McDonalds in Ironwood, Richmond, B.C. Its a really good place to go for coffee, a snack, or a meal. I would highly recommend it!!!
Nice playground
Always good to go to McDonalds. They renovated this place and it looks way better now.
The coffee here is always fresh and not watered down like other locations
Whole day service good place for coffee
Quite fast and good behaviour. Most importantly, its conveniently located at the big strip mall.
Clean and good service
Good size play place for kids . Not small like some of the other McDonalds.
Staff are nice. Clean place
Its McDonalds. Does it need a review. Best fries in the world!;
Nice facility: Clean, easy accessibility, play area for kids, attentive staff.
Mcdonalds has a very special place in my heart. Always a 5 star experience.

reviews.reviewer_name: Moe Leghari At Sutton Group - Seafair Realty
reviews.review_text: I personally found Alisha provided amazing service!
Ordered through McD App. Quick and easy. No Hassle.
Love the $1 iced coffee promo right now.
Good service. Same food as all the other McDonalds
Very busy location. Staff works tirelessly to keep the ongoing waves of customers Mchappy.
Cool place. Service is fast and amicable
Super friendly and fast service, great guys work there! Thank you
excellent, friendly and fast service.
Great location service and food. Amazing coffee
Beat restaurant always good staff needs better hygiene standards
Great service and food quality is pretty good
Always tasty pop!!  They have the mix just right.
Surprisingly good service for such a busy McDonald s.
Always busy but got in and out pretty quick.
How can you go wrong with ANY size coffee for a $1?
had a pleasant experience here. will return when back in town
Amazing workers only thing that can improve is parking
Good fast friendly service and staff are very helpful.
Nice place and faster just no have playground
One short young gentleman had amazing service
Im loving it.... Well, my kids do anyway
Fast service and good quality for McDonalds
Its fast ,hot food fun place
Needs Level 2 electric car recharging plugs on their parking lot.
Fast service. Happy workers always smiling.
This location is clean, service efficient, and friendly.
Good place
Fast, accurate service
Some times I just need a Big Mac!
Good/decent food!
Has a nice play area for the kids
Very good breakfast sandwich
Quick convenient and always consistent.
